# Backend Standards

- Stack baseline: NestJS + GraphQL + Prisma + PostgreSQL.
- Keep business logic in services; resolvers/controllers stay thin.
- Use Prisma transactions for multi-step writes (order/payment flows).
- Money fields are integer cents; avoid floating-point amounts.
- Add idempotency for order/payment creation endpoints.

## Data and Errors

- Validate all external inputs (DTO/schema guards).
- Use explicit domain errors and map them to stable API responses.
- Record important state transitions (order lifecycle logs/events).
- Keep migrations deterministic and reviewed before applying.
